  <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdate.maint2">
  <title>Next, 2013 (Maintenance Update) </title>
   
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
   <term>Managing Networks</term>
   <listitem>
    <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
      <para>Added a section about managing networks to <xref
       linkend="cha.adm.cli"/>.</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para><xref linkend="sec.user.dash.networks"/> has been enhanced.</para>
     </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
   </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>High-level User Roles</term>
    <listitem><para>Added definition of user roles to <xref
    linkend="pre.cloud.admin"/>.</para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para><xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>: Added image requirements for
        use with &vmware; (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=838040"/>).</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para><xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>: Added image requirements for
        use with &hyper; (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765"/>).</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para><xref linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.upload"/> and <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.props.modify"/>: Added hypervisor-specific
        example commands for image upload and modification of image properties
         (<ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=838040"/> and
         <ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765"
         />).</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para><xref linkend="tip.adm.img.req.virt.mult"/>: Added section on how
        to configure images for use with multiple hypervisors. (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765#c22"/>)</para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect1>
  
  <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdate.gm">
   <title>September 11, 2013 (Initial Release) </title>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>&ostack; Service Names</term>
     <listitem>
      <!--state if new or updated, if applicable, add number of bug, fate,
      or doc comment for reference-->
      <para>Replaced code names with the &ostack; services' real names,
       according to <ulink
        url="https://wiki.openstack.org/wiki/Documentation/Conventions#General_style_conventions"
       />. For example, talk of <emphasis>&ostack; &img;</emphasis>
       instead of <emphasis>&o_img;</emphasis>.</para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>Update to &ostack; Grizzly</term>
     <listitem>
      <para>The &dash; and the command line chapter have been updated to
       the &ostack; Grizzly release on which &productname; 2.0 is based. This
       includes the following changes:</para>
      <itemizedlist>
       <listitem>
        <para>The following section has been added: <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.dash.networks"/>.</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>Some categories have been added to the &dash;'s main screen,
         others changed name. Most importantly, the download option for RC files
         can now be found in the <guimenu>Access &amp; Security</guimenu>
         category. See <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.intro"/> and <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.cli.rc"/>.</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>Image upload is now also possible via the &dash;, though with
         limited options. For details, refer to <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.img"
         /></para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>The compute, memory, and storage capacity of the default flavors
         has changed. For details, refer to <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.flavors"
         /> or <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.flavors"/>.</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>The workflow for some tasks has changed, most notably for the
         following ones: <xref linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.create"/>, and <xref
          linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.assign"/>, .</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>In addition to <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.general"
          xrefstyle="select:title nopage"/>, hypervisor-specific requirements
         have been added. Refer to <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>.</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>&susestudio; and &suseonsite; now have better integration
         with &productname;. For details, refer to <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.cli.img.build"/>.</para>
       </listitem>
       <listitem>
        <para>To make sure that an image is only launched on appropriate
         hypervisors, you can specify respective properties that the image
         requires. For details, refer to <xref
          linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.props.modify"/>. </para>
       </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
